name: KAREEM. CHRISTOPHER'S SON.
description:
This is Kareem. He was so nervous to write for me. He asked me to walk away, not look and promise not to read the page until I got home. I took his photo, and then did as he asked.
He was a very timid child so I wanted to make him as comfortable as possible. His dad, Christopher, also helped out. He encouraged Kareem to take the photos and write whatever he liked.
